$ lsb_release -a
No LSB modules are available.
Distributor ID: Ubuntu
Description:    Ubuntu 20.04.4 LTS
Release:        20.04
Codename:       focal

$ deno --version
deno 1.22.1 (release, x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu)
v8 10.3.174.6
typescript 4.6.2
```

